name: Aoi Okuyama taki giri framed
description: Second NFT of this work, now with more experience in the field, I bring the work with higher resolution and frame, to the #HENthousand event - Traditional painting on wooden canvas with acrylic paint and ink, textured art with stone powder, measure 36 x 27 cm. Work Aoi Okuyama taki giri - iagoDS - Brazil - tt @iagods_ / ig @iagods_artes - Segundo NFT desta obra, agora com mais experiência no ramo de NFTs, trago a obra com maior resolução e com moldura, para o evento #HENthousand - Pintura tradicional sobre tela de madeira com Tinta acrílica e nanquim, arte texturizada com pó de pedra, medida 36 x 27 cm.
